Use the standard library
This is how to specialFilter of nums:
   Remember that count is 0
   Remember that n is nums's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that x is item i in nums
      When x is more than 9, then:
         Remember that last is remainder of x and 10
         Remember that first is x
         Do this 100 times:
            When first is less than 10, then:
               Leave the loop
            End when
            Remember that first is quotient of first and 10
         End do
         When first is 1, then:
            When last is 5, then:
               Increase count
            End when
         End when
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is count
